#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:63
msgid ""
"dnfdragora is a DNF frontend, based on Mageia rpmdragora layout and Fedora "
"yumex-dnf interaction with dnfdaemon.<br><br>"
msgstr ""
"dnfdragora on DNF-i kasutajaliides, mis tugineb Msgeia rpmdragora "
"paigutusele ja Fedora yumex-dnf'i koostööle dnfdaemon'iga <br><br>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:64
msgid ""
"dnfdragora is basically a package manager user interface that allows you to "
"install, update, remove, and search for packages and more.<br><br>"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:65
msgid ""
"dnfdragora is part of manatools and it is based on manatools.aui so that it "
"can work using Qt (PySide6), GTK 4, or ncurses, i.e. both graphical and "
"textual user interfaces.<br><br>"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:66
msgid "dnfdragora window is comprised of:"
msgstr "dnfdragora aknas leiab:"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:71
msgid "Menu bar content"
msgstr "Menüüriba sisu"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:73
msgid "Menu bar contains dnfdragora drop down menus:"
msgstr "Menüüriba sisaldab dnfdragora ripikmenüüsid:"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:81
msgid "File Menu"
msgstr "Failimenüü"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:83
msgid "<h2>Reset selection</h2>"
msgstr "<h2>Lähtesta valik</h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:84
msgid ""
"This menu removes any flags on packages; if any packages have been selected "
"for installation or removal, they will be reset to their previous status.<br>"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:85
msgid "<h2>Refresh metadata</h2>"
msgstr "<h2>Värskenda metaandmeid</h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:86
msgid ""
"This menu sends a request to dnfdaemon to force a refresh of all the "
"metadata. This action is asynchronous and requires rebuilding the package "
"information cache.<br>"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:87
msgid "<h2>Repositories</h2>"
msgstr "<h2>Hoidlad</h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:88
msgid ""
"This menu opens a dialog that allows you to enable or disable repositories. "
"Any changes are valid only while dnfdragora is running and are not permanent."
"<br>"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:89
msgid "<h2>Quit</h2>"
msgstr "<h2>Välju</h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:90
msgid "This menu exits from dnfdragora.<br>"
msgstr "See menüü lõpetab dnfdragora töö <br>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:97
msgid "Information Menu"
msgstr "Teabemenüü"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:99
msgid "<h2>History</h2>"
msgstr "<h2>Ajalugu</h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:100
msgid ""
"This menu runs a dialog containing transaction history shown in a tree "
"ordered by date. Selected history can be undone by pressing <b>Undo</b> "
"button.<br>"
msgstr ""
"See menüü avab tehingute ajaloo, mis on korraldatud kuupäevade järgi "
"puustruktuuri. Valitud ajalookirjet saab tühistada klõpsuga nupule <b>Võta "
"tagasi</b> <br>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:101
msgid ""
"<br><i>Note that this function is currently broken because of a DNF API "
"change</i><br>"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:108
msgid "Option Menu"
msgstr "Valikumenüü"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:110
msgid "<h2>User preferences</h2>"
msgstr "<h2>Kasutaja eelistused</h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:111
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This menu opens a %s containing user settings to customize dnfdragora "
"behavior.<br>"
msgstr ""
"See menüü avab %s, mis susaldab dnfdragora käitumist mõjutavaid kasutaja "
"seadistusi <br>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:111
msgid "dialog"
msgstr "dialoogi"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:119
msgid ""
"This dialog allows to customize dnfdragora behavior by changing options. "
"Some changes are available after closing the dialog, others need a "
"dnfdragora restart.<br><br>"
msgstr ""
"See dialoog  võimaldab kohandada dnfdragora käitumist valikuid muutes. Mõned "
"muudatused hakkavad kehtima pärast dialoogi sulgemist, mõned alles pärast "
"dnfdragora taaskäivitamist.<br><br>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:120
msgid "<h2>System options</h2>"
msgstr "<h2> Süsteemi valikud </h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:121
msgid ""
"<ul><li><b>Run transactions on packages automatically without confirmation "
"needed</b>: if checked transactions do not need to be confirmed, dnfdragora "
"works as answering always <i>yes</i>."
msgstr ""
"<ul><li><b>Paketitehingute automaatne käivitamine ilma kinnitust nõudmata</"
"b> :märkimise korral ei ole tarvis tehinguid kinnitada, dnfdragora töötab, "
"nagi vastataks alati  <i>jah</i>."

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:122
msgid ""
"<br><b>NOTE</b> that this option means that also removing packages is "
"silently accepted</li>"
msgstr ""
"<br><b>PANGE TÄHELE,</b>et see valik tähendab ühtlasi pakettide vaikimisi, "
"kinnituseta eemaldamise  lubamist</li>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:123
msgid ""
"<li><b>Consider packages to upgrade as updates</b>: if checked upgrades are "
"added to updates and filtered as updates.</li>"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:124
msgid ""
"<li><b>Hide dnfdragora-update menu if there are no updates</b>: if checked "
"dnfdragora update is hidden if there are no updates."
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:125
msgid ""
"<br><b>NOTE</b> that this option is experimental, not all desktops manage it "
"as expected</li>"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:126
msgid ""
"<li><b>Interval to check for updates</b>: the given number represents how "
"often dnfdragora checks for updates; the value is expressed in minutes</li>"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:127
msgid ""
"<li><b>Metadata expire time</b>: time to force Metadata expiration, the "
"value is expressed in hours</li></ul>"
msgstr ""
"<li><b>Metaandmete aegumise aeg </b>: aeg tundides. mille järel metaandmed "
"sunnitakse aeguma</li></ul>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:128
msgid "<h2>Layout options</h2>"
msgstr "<h2> Paigutusvalikud </h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:129
msgid ""
"<ul><li><b>Show updates</b>: if checked dnfdragora starts with <i>updates</"
"i> filter active, i.e. showing only package available for updates if any.</"
"li>"
msgstr ""
"<ul><li><b>Uuenduste näitamine</b>: märkimise korral käivitatakse dnfdragora "
"aktiivse <i>uuenduste</i>filtriga, see tähendab näidatakse ainult pakette, "
"mida saab uuendada, kui neid peaks leiduma.</li>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:130
msgid ""
"<li><b>Do not show groups view</b>: filtering by groups could require CPU if "
"using comps, if this option is checked dnfdragora starts showing all "
"packages.</li></ul>"
msgstr ""
"<li><b> Rühmavaadet ei näidata </b>: rühmade kaupa filtreerimine nõuab "
"comps'i kasutamisel omajagu peotsessorivõimsust. M'rkimise korral näidatakse "
"dnfdragora käivitamisel kõiki pakette.</li> </ul>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:131
msgid "<b>NOTE</b> that the above options require dnfdragora to be restarted."
msgstr ""
"<b>PANGE TÄHELE</b>, et eeltoodud valikud nõuavad rakendamiseks dnfdragora "
"taaskäivitamist."

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:132
msgid "<h2>Search options</h2>"
msgstr "<h2>Otsinguvalikud</h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:133
msgid ""
"<ul><li><b>Show newest packages only</b>: if checked dnfdragora shows only "
"newest packages on search.</li>"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:134
msgid ""
"<li><b>Fuzzy search (legacy mode)</b>: if checked a search without using "
"regular expressions will add \"*\" to the given words, restoring the "
"behavior dnfdragora had using dnfdaemon 4.</li></ul>"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:135
msgid "<h2>Logging options</h2>"
msgstr "<h2>Logmisvalikud</h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:136
msgid ""
"Enable these options to let dnfdragora log on file called <i>dnfdragora.log</"
"i>."
msgstr ""
"Nende valikute lubamine võimaldab dnfdragoral logida faili nimega "
"<i>dnfdragora.log</i>."

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:137
msgid ""
"<ul><li><b>Change directory</b>: this option allows you to set the logging "
"directory; the directory must exist and needs write permission.</li>"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:138
msgid ""
"<li><b>Debug level</b>: if checked, verbose logging is enabled.</li></ul>"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:146
msgid "Help Menu"
msgstr "Abimenüü"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:148
msgid "<h2>Manual</h2>"
msgstr "<h2>Käsiraamat</h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:149
msgid "This menu opens dnfdragora help dialog."
msgstr "See menüü avab dnfdragora abidialoogi."

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:150
msgid "<h2>About</h2>"
msgstr "<h2>Teave</h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:151
msgid "This menu opens dnfdragora about dialog."
msgstr "See menüü avsb dnfdragora teabedialoogi."

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:159
msgid "Views and search"
msgstr "Vaated ja otsing"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:161
msgid "<h2>Views</h2>"
msgstr "<h2>Vaated</h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:162
msgid ""
"The first combobox allows you to show packages by groups. If <i>Groups</i> "
"is selected, the group panel shows a tree view containing groups, and "
"selecting a group shows related packages in the package panel."
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:163
msgid "If <i>All</i> is selected, the package panel contains all the packages."
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:164
msgid "<h2>Filters</h2>"
msgstr "<h2>Filtrid</h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:165
msgid ""
"The Filter combobox allows you to filter the packages shown in the package "
"panel by:"
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:166
msgid "<ul><li><b>Installed</b>: shows installed packages only.</li>"
msgstr ""
"<ul><li><b>Paigaldatud</b>: näidatakse ainult paigaldatud pakette.</li>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:167
msgid "<li><b>Not installed</b>: shows available packages only.</li>"
msgstr "<li><b>Paigaldamata</b>: näidatakse ainult saadaolevaid pakette.</li>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:168
msgid ""
"<li><b>To update</b>: shows packages that are available for updates only.</"
"li>"
msgstr ""
"<li><b>Uuendatavad</b>: näidatakse ainult pakette, millele on uendusi.</li>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:169
msgid ""
"<li><b>Show x86_64 and noarch only</b>: if dnfdragora is running on x86_64 "
"architecture, it hides i686 packages.</li>"
msgstr ""
"<li><b>Ainult x86_64 ja noarch</b>: kui dnfdragora töötab  x86_64 "
"arhitektuuri peal, peidetakse i686 paketid.</li>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:170
msgid ""
"<li><b>All</b>: shows all the packages, i.e. available, updates and "
"installed.</li></ul>"
msgstr ""
"<li><b>Kõik</b>: näidatakse kõiki pakette, see tähendab saadaolevaid, "
"uuendatavaid kui ka paigaldatuid.</li></ul>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:171
msgid "<h2>Search</h2>"
msgstr "<h2>Otsing</h2>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:172
msgid ""
"Search is performed by pressing the <i>Search</i> button when the text field "
"is not empty. The Search combobox allows you to search the given text in "
"package <i>names</i>, <i>summaries</i>, <i>descriptions</i>, or <i>files</i>."
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:173
msgid ""
"A special checkbox <i>Use regexp</i> is used to look for packages by python "
"language regular expressions. This search is performed on cached package "
"information such as for the <b>only names and summaries</b>."
msgstr ""
"Spetsiaalne märkekast  <i>Regulaaravaldise kasutamine</i> võimaldab pakette "
"otsida Pythoni regulaarvaldisi ksutades. Selline otsing sooitatakse "
"pakettide puhverdtud teabe peal, näiteks <b>ainult nimedes ja kokkuvõtetes</"
"b>."

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:174
msgid ""
"<i>Note</i>: when regular expressions are used to search by name, the full "
"package filename including the version is used."
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:175
msgid "The <i>Clear search</i> button resets search text field."
msgstr "Nupuga <i>Puhasta otsing</i> saab tekstivälja lähtestada."

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:185
msgid ""
"This panel shows all the groups available to filter packages, if the Groups "
"view is selected. The special group <i>Search</i> is added after a search is "
"performed."
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:195
msgid ""
"This panel shows all the filtered packages with their basic information such "
"as <i>name</i>, <i>summary</i>, <i>version</i>, <i>release</i>, "
"<i>architecture</i>, <i>size</i>, and <i>status</i>."
msgstr ""

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:196
msgid ""
"A checkbox for any packages is available to add related package to "
"transaction for installing, updating or removing."
msgstr ""
"Kõigi pakettide juures on märkekast, millega saab määrata paigaldamise, "
"uuendamise või eemaldamise tehingu,"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:206
msgid ""
"This panel shows all the package information such as <i>description</i>, "
"<i>URL</i>, <i>repository</i>, <i>requirements</i>, <i>file list</i>, and "
"<i>changelog</i>."
msgstr ""
"Sellel paneelil näeb kogu paketi teavet, see tähendab <i>kirjeldust</i>, "
"<i>URL-i</i>, <i>hoidlat</i>, <i>sõltuvusi</i>, <i>faillde loendit</i> ja "
"<i>muudatuste logi</i>."

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:207
msgid ""
"<br><br><i>Note that changelog is not provided by dnfdaemon at the moment.</"
"i>"
msgstr ""
"<br><br><i>Pange tähele, et praegu  dnfdaemon muudatuste logi ei näita.</i>"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:215
msgid "Progress bar"
msgstr "Edenemistriba"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:217
msgid ""
"Progress bar shows dnfdragora operations progression such as transactions "
"and caching data."
msgstr ""
"Edenemirtiba näitab dnfdragora toimingute, näiteks tehingute ja andmete "
"puhverdamise edenemist."

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:225
msgid "Buttons line"
msgstr "Nupurida"

#: dnfdragora/helpinfo.py:227
msgid ""
"<ul><li><b>Apply</b>: when some packages are selected for installing or "
"updating or deselected for uninstalling this button runs the transaction to "
